HEADWORD: Eagre
<hw>Ea"gre</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>e⟦aacute⟧gor</ets>, <ets><?/gor</ets>, in comp., water, sea,
